   Workaround: Disable SubagentStop hooks
   - Modify .claude/settings.json
   - Modify ~/.claude/settings.json

   Apply workaround? [Y/n]
   (Will be stored for future auto-apply)"

  :workaround-applied
  "✅ Workaround applied successfully
   Updated: .claude/settings.json
